    "Schliemann unearthed and important late Bronze Age palace, which he published in his 1885 <em>Tiryns: The Prehistoric Palace of the Kings of Tiryns</em>.": [],
    "Once more he returned to Hissarlik in 1889-90.": [],
    "He attempted to purchase the land of the Knossos site in Crete, but was unsuccessful.": [],
    "He died in Naples the same year.": [],
    "So much of Schliemann was deception and ruthless enthusiasm that his accomplishments are difficult to evaluate.": [],
